1051→
1052→// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1053→// Intelligence: Session End Helpers
1054→// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1055→
1056→/**
1057→ * End an agent session by setting ended_at, simulating what the CLI/orchestrator does.
1058→ * This triggers the SurrealDB EVENT for Observer session-end analysis.
